<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ نُصَيْبٌ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - وَإِنِّي وَإِيَّاهُمْ كَسَاعٍ لِقَاعِدٍ ... مُقِيمِ وَأَشْقَى النَّاسِ بِالشِّعْرِ قَائِلُهْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
