<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُ:</span> <span class="c2">(مجزوء الخفيف)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ - اِسْلَمِي أُمَّ خَالِدٍ ... رُبَّ سَاعٍ لقَاعِدِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
