<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ إِسْمَاعِيلُ بْنُ يَسارٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(الوافر)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
